				<div class="col-md-12">
					<h2>Art</h2>
					<p>We marry form and function. Our symmetrical team of artistic and technical talent means we build products with functional elegance and tasteful aesthetics.</p>
				</div>
			</div>
			<div class="row feature backwards">
				<div class="col-md-6 info">
					<h4>Applied Sensory</h4>
					<p>Applied Sensory is a consulting company which provides product evaluation for the wine, beer and olive oil industry.</p>
					<p>Applied Sensory was contributing to a publication on olive oil production. We were hired to create a map which illustrates the olive oil growing regions of California. The illustration was done to scale and in a style which matched the academic feel of the publication.</p>
				</div>
				<div class="col-md-6 image">
					<img src="images/california-map.jpg" class="img-responsive" alt="California Olive Oil Map" />
				</div>
			</div>
