				<div class="col-md-6 info">
					<h4>Crush Challenge</h4>
					<p>Produced in partnership between Amgen, Dempsey Center for Cancer Hope & Healing and ZD Wines. The Crush Challenge is a charity bicycle ride in the heart of Napa Valley.</p>
					<p>Crush Challenge needed a way to photograph the event and publish images online in real time. We devised a system which allowed our photographers to upload content to a public folder straight from camera. From there event promoters distributed our work to a variety of social media channels.</p>
				</div>
				<div class="col-md-6 image">
					<img src="images/partick-dempsey.jpg" class="img-responsive" alt="Patrick Dempsey Crush Challenge" />
				</div>
			</div>
