				<div class="col-md-6 info">
					<h4>Graphic Design</h4>
					<p>Graphic design is the methodology of visual communication, and problem-solving through the use of type, space and image.</p>
					<p>Good design can make information easy to process which ultimately leaves your audience with a more memorable and impact experience. Design can also help shift your image which allows you to capture new market areas and find new consumers.</p>
				</div>
				<div class="col-md-6 image">
					<img src="images/zd-wines-designs.jpg" class="img-responsive" alt="ZD Wines Graphic Design Marketing Collateral" />
				</div>
			</div>
