				<div class="col-md-6 info">
					<h4>Grgich Hills</h4>
					<p>Grigich Hills is a winery in the Rutherford region of Napa Valley. Notable founder Mike Grigich is the winemaker behind the 1973 Chateau Montelena Chardonnay that bested several Burgundy wines in the Judgement of Paris.</p>
					<p>Grigich Hills hired us to start an image database for their chocolate festival. These images would be used to promote future festivals both online and in print material.</p>
				</div>
